AI PROJECT STARTER — INITIALIZATION PROMPT
==========================================

Copy and paste this entire prompt to Claude Code to initialize your project.
(Use this if /init-project command is not working)

---

Please help me set up my project using the ai-project-starter template.

Ask me these questions one at a time:
1. What's the name of my project?
2. What type is it? (web-fullstack / api-only / mobile / automation / library / other)
3. What's my preferred tech stack?
4. Which features do I need? (auth, database, payments, email, CI/CD, docker)
5. What's my experience level with Claude Code? (beginner / intermediate / advanced)
6. Do I want to start from a blueprint? (next-saas / api-service / automation / none)

After I answer all questions:
- Configure CLAUDE.md with my project info
- Configure AGENTS.md with my architecture
- Set up memory/MEMORY.md and memory/sprint.md
- Generate appropriate .gitignore
- Create any feature-specific files
- Initialize git with first commit
- Show me a summary and next steps

Start by asking question 1.
